  "description": "Okay, we have this brain feature called knowledge, and we also have this page called decisions. I would like to combine those two concepts. We also have this notion of pages, similar to the Notion app, and I think it would be helpful to consolidate knowledge into pages. Any knowledge we have would go into a page, and any decisions we'd have would go into a page.\n\nI also would like to explore combining the smart labels with pages so that a page itself would be a smart label. I could customize the page, choose the color of the page, and then choose what rule there is for that page and then knowledge and decisions. Any email summaries would be added to the page. Not exactly sure what that would look like, but the idea is that people would go to pages for their knowledge, and that we would leverage that concept of the smart labels so that the AI would know what page to add to. We can incorporate subpages to be able to differentiate between knowledge and decisions, but that would be the general idea. ",
