  "justFinishedAt": "2026-03-08T03:59:42.134Z",
  "summary": "## Summary: Unified Pages with Knowledge, Decisions & Smart Labels\n\n### Changes Implemented\n\n**Core Architecture — Pages as Smart-Label-Powered Knowledge Containers:**\n- Extended the `pages` database table with smart label fields: `pageType` (page/knowledge/decisions), `color` (hex), `smartRule` (AI classification prompt), `smartActive` (auto-classify toggle)\n- Created new `pageEntries` table for storing knowledge items, decisions, email summaries, and manual notes within pages\n- Added `pageTypeEnum` and `pageEntryTypeEnum` PostgreSQL enums\n- Full RLS policies on `pageEntries` using workspace ownership subquery pattern\n\n**API Routes:**\n- `GET/POST /api/pages/[pageId]/entries` — List and create page entries with filtering by type\n- `PATCH/DELETE /api/pages/entries/[entryId]` — Update and delete individual entries\n- Updated `POST /api/pages` to accept `page_type`, `color`, `smart_rule`, `smart_active`\n- Updated `PATCH /api/pages/[pageId]` to accept same new fields\n- Updated `GET /api/pages/[pageId]` to return entries and entry count for knowledge/decisions pages\n\n**TypeScript Types:**\n- Added `PageType`, `PageEntryType`, `PageEntry`, `PageWithEntries` types\n- Updated `Page` interface with `pageType`, `color`, `smartRule`, `smartActive` fields\n\n**React Hooks:**\n- Added `usePageEntries`, `useCreatePageEntry`, `useUpdatePageEntry`, `useDeletePageEntry` hooks\n- Updated `useCreatePage` and `useUpdatePage` to support new page fields\n\n**UI Components:**\n- **PageEntriesView** — New component for viewing/adding entries in knowledge & decisions pages, with type filtering, entry cards with badges, expandable details, and an add entry modal\n- **PageHeader** — Updated with color picker (12 preset colors), smart rule configuration panel with active toggle, and page type badge\n- **PagesSidebar** — Updated tree items to show colored dots for pages with colors, type-appropriate icons (🧠 knowledge, ⚖️ decisions), and a \"New Page\" dropdown menu offering Blank Page, Knowledge Page, and Decisions Page creation\n- **PageView** — Updated to render `PageEntriesView` for knowledge/decisions page types\n\n**Navigation & Integration:**\n- Brain page Knowledge tab now shows a banner: \"Organize knowledge into pages with smart rules\" with a link to Pages\n- Decisions page now shows a banner: \"Decisions can now be organized into Pages\" with a link to Pages\n- Both existing features remain fully functional while the new Pages system provides a unified organization layer\n\n### Files Modified\n- `lib/db/schema.ts` — Added `pageTypeEnum`, `pageEntryTypeEnum`, new columns on `pages`, new `pageEntries` table\n- `types/index.ts` — Added `PageType`, `PageEntryType`, `PageEntry`, `PageWithEntries`, updated `Page`\n- `lib/hooks/usePages.ts` — Added entries hooks, updated existing hooks with new fields\n- `app/api/pages/route.ts` — Extended POST with new page fields\n- `app/api/pages/[pageId]/route.ts` — Extended PATCH and GET with new fields and entries\n- `components/pages/PageHeader.tsx` — Color picker, smart rule config, page type badge\n- `components/pages/PagesSidebar.tsx` — Color dots, type icons, new page type dropdown\n- `components/pages/PageEntriesView.tsx` — New entries view component\n- `app/(app)/workspace/[workspaceId]/[pageId]/page.tsx` — Conditional rendering for entries pages\n- `app/(app)/brain/page.tsx` — Pages integration banner on Knowledge tab\n- `app/(app)/decisions/page.tsx` — Pages integration banner\n\n### Files Created\n- `app/api/pages/[pageId]/entries/route.ts` — Page entries list/create API\n- `app/api/pages/entries/[entryId]/route.ts` — Page entry update/delete API\n- `components/pages/PageEntriesView.tsx` — Entries view component\n\n### Notes for Developer\n- **Database migration needed**: Run `drizzle-kit generate` and `drizzle-kit push` to create the new `page_type` enum, `page_entry_type` enum, new columns on `pages` table, and the `page_entries` table. Since drizzle-kit doesn't read `.env.local`, pass `DATABASE_URL` inline.\n- **Smart rule classification**: The `smartRule` and `smartActive` fields on pages are ready for integration with the existing smart labels classification engine (`lib/smartLabels/classify.ts`). When implementing auto-classification, call the AI with the page's `smartRule` prompt to determine whether incoming content should be added as an entry.\n- **Existing data**: The standalone Decisions page and Brain Knowledge tab continue to work independently. Migration of existing data (brain thoughts → knowledge page entries, decisions → decisions page entries) can be done incrementally.\n- The unique index on `page_entries(page_id, source_type, source_id)` leverages PostgreSQL's NULL-distinct behavior — manual entries (null source) are not constrained, while source-linked entries prevent duplicates."
}